Manking
Dearcet Dibs.
Not much chance to
write so
shing fame eitter chich will gur
my going and doing.
has asked for you lots g to be
Mr Johnson
and bus Peck
also. In Hoem too asked to br_
remembard
to you and the gires, Dus Holm
is ill in
Hankors.
an having dinner tomoro
with sidney Lafoon -
he
sint his
bist to
you
and the gees. I must remember te
aste him abor
It Ruths picture
book and
try to git one for
her
Max Polin
hao bun
herr for sense
dap, It dror up by car with allon.
The latter took a job with Pawley to go
to Harkow and teat fly a Vultre. He
found that he could not sail his boat
around the boom in the champoo.
vor didnt ser him because he wint to
Hankow while ur cars Enroute here. May
droor back to Shanghai today. AL say.
Welly is back in Shanghai
and is freling
fine.
her acturtee..
The gaps an not bombing Nanking
any mor
so thirs nothing to worry about
When they
allack this city they confine
ther bombing to the airports and the
railroad.
Its mid-night so must to
bed- al my loor to you and lot, to the
gues -
Mom - Had
